{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159860/extras/MegabeamButterfly.gif?t=1733959893\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A FULLY WOOLY WORLD</strong>\u00a0</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Retro-arcade meets cozy gaming in Feltopia, a stop-motion side-scroller made entirely out of wool. You are Skyrider, a magical sheep herder on a quest to protect their rainbow flock from an infectious Smog Spirit.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIND AND PROTECT YOUR FLOCK!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More sheep = more powers! They've been scattered across the vast world of Feltopia and infected by smog. Transform them and keep them safe by gathering them into a cozy bundle!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong> CAST SPELLS &amp; WATCH THE WORLD TRANSFORM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cast your rainbow magic to heal the infected beings of Feltopia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159860/extras/electricskiesflying.gif?t=1733959893\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BATTLE &amp; HEAL BOSSES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Guardians of the Realms have been deeply affected by the infectious smog. Solve simple puzzles and wield your growing powers to restore them to their true forms.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159860/extras/AquilaRainbowStill.jpg?t=1733959893\" /> <strong>The future of Feltopia depends on you....</strong> <br>   <br>  <strong>WARNING: Playing FELTOPIA may result in fuzzy feelings.</strong>   <br>   </h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159860/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733959893","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159860/page.bg.jpg?t=1733959893","capsule_